			<wp:comment_content><![CDATA[When Harvard did not come,  what else came? It's lovely,  but every time,  while looking down,  and at the same time going forward,  one may hit a brick wall.  It may be an time then to look at the wall again,  and decide whether to go back,  some paces,  and run at the wall with more speed and momentum,  or even turn left,  or right,  and go around the wall,  and get to the other side of the wall by going around the sides.  

